<title>USA: Boston Sci. gains lost ground after results.</title>
<headline>Boston Sci. gains lost ground after results.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Boston Scientific Corp shares shot up 15 percent in heated trade Wednesday as investors, relieved at no negative surprises in last night's quarterly earnings report, went bargain hunting.</p>
<p>&quot;People were waiting to see what was said in the quarterly (results conference) call (last night), (with) buyers making sure there was nothing surprising,&quot; said an analyst who declined to be identified.</p>
<p>&quot;At these levels the stock is selling at a low multiple to its growth rate, so there is pent-up demand for it,&quot; he said.</p>
</text>
